<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="yell-v">yell <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /jel/    美 /jel/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vi-vt">1.★ <strong>vi &amp; vt 叫喊；大声喊 (说)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>“Help me!”she <strong>yelled at the top of</strong> her <strong>voice</strong> (= very loudly).
“救救我！”她声嘶力竭地喊道。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>yell (sth) at sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He yelled at her to be careful. 
他大声叫她小心。</p></div></div>